From: Sam Ravnborg <>
Subject: Re: [PATCH 2.6.21.3] kbuild: fix build for cygwin
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
